1
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:32,980
=The Secret of the Lost Pearl=

2
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:34,940
=Episode 15=
(Fiction. Do not imitate.)

3
00:00:41,750 --> 00:00:43,243
Captain, the road ahead has collapsed.

4
00:00:43,350 --> 00:00:44,200
Pass the word down.

5
00:00:44,350 --> 00:00:46,200
- Move on foot.
- Yes.

6
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:47,160
No matter what,

7
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:49,600
not a single relic
can leave Xuanyi County.

8
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:50,500
Search carefully.

9
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:51,960
- Don't miss any corner.
- Move.

10
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:52,840
- Yes.
- Yes.

11
00:00:53,790 --> 00:00:54,630
Hurry.

12
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:59,880
Ms. He, you really saved us this time.

13
00:01:00,016 --> 00:01:01,200
If you had not stolen the box,

14
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,323
we'd all have died in there.

15
00:01:02,750 --> 00:01:03,590
Wait.

16
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:04,840
What are you doing?

17
00:01:05,230 --> 00:01:06,230
What did I tell you?

18
00:01:06,230 --> 00:01:07,080
Is this how

19
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:07,950
you looked after her?

20
00:01:08,230 --> 00:01:09,560
She almost got her head blown off.

21
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:11,280
Why?

22
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,886
Because she was trying to save you.

23
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:14,150
To save you, Lu almost died.

24
00:01:14,150 --> 00:01:15,040
Something about that.

25
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:17,000
Calm down.

26
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,280
Let me say something fair.

27
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:20,000
If Chubby had not put the bomb there,

28
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,989
we'd still be chased by Huang Long.

29
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,629
Why didn't you negotiate
with Huang Long?

30
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:24,710
Why send a woman to do it?

31
00:01:24,950 --> 00:01:26,280
Are you even being reasonable?

32
00:01:26,790 --> 00:01:27,640
- You...
- Stop!

33
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,490
You want to fight?

34
00:01:28,490 --> 00:01:29,340
Chen Youxi.

35
00:01:29,533 --> 00:01:30,590
- Calm down.
- Chen Youxi.

36
00:01:30,590 --> 00:01:31,430
Chen Youxi.

37
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,200
- What are you doing?
- Lu is a coward.

38
00:01:33,310 --> 00:01:35,150
He nearly lost his life
trying to save you.

39
00:01:35,230 --> 00:01:36,280
Say something about that.

40
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:37,760
You only value Ms. He,

41
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:39,480
but the two of us can die, right?

42
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,400
Get lost.

43
00:01:40,950 --> 00:01:42,150
- Stop.
- Don't pull me.

44
00:01:42,150 --> 00:01:43,280
Say that again if you dare.

45
00:01:43,310 --> 00:01:44,200
Calm down.

46
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,430
- Why do this?
- Calm down.

47
00:01:45,430 --> 00:01:46,400
I am perfectly fine.

48
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,333
You're really not hurt?

49
00:01:52,870 --> 00:01:53,710
I'm fine.

50
00:01:53,870 --> 00:01:54,710
How about you?

51
00:01:55,070 --> 00:01:56,950
You just fell. Are you okay?

52
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:00,840
- You...
- It was great.

53
00:02:01,350 --> 00:02:02,870
We had a lovely conversation.

54
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:07,680
Miss Bai, I've been meaning to ask you.

55
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:09,520
What is inside that box

56
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,820
that made your group fall apart?

57
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:11,840
I already asked her.

58
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,326
She said she doesn't know.

59
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,870
I was asking her.

60
00:02:18,470 --> 00:02:19,910
Just like Chen Youxi said,

61
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,800
I don't know

62
00:02:22,030 --> 00:02:22,963
what is inside the box.

63
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:24,930
Do you think

64
00:02:24,940 --> 00:02:25,840
I'd believe that?

65
00:02:26,750 --> 00:02:27,876
We talked about this too.

66
00:02:27,887 --> 00:02:29,373
Huang believes that was the true hall.

67
00:02:29,384 --> 00:02:30,848
The box was placed inside the coffin

68
00:02:30,859 --> 00:02:32,019
with an eyeball pattern on it.

69
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:33,870
He thinks it is exactly
what their boss wants.

70
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:35,520
I said it already.

71
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,030
I am asking Miss Bai.

72
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:42,120
I have already told Chen Youxi
everything I know.

73
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:43,960
If you still have questions,

74
00:02:44,190 --> 00:02:45,240
you can ask him.

75
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:52,710
Why does this sound like jealousy?

76
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:55,910
If I had known,
I'd have fallen with Bai Lingling.

77
00:02:56,190 --> 00:02:57,840
Chen Youxi could stay with Ms. He,

78
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,946
and we wouldn't be fighting.

79
00:02:59,870 --> 00:03:00,800
Dream on.

80
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:03,590
Fine.

81
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,630
Since you refuse to say anything,

82
00:03:05,915 --> 00:03:06,889
there is no reason for us

83
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:07,970
to keep traveling together.

84
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,080
Why not split up here

85
00:03:10,397 --> 00:03:11,410
and go our separate ways?

86
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,750
How would we split?

87
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:18,560
There is only one passage.

88
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:20,186
Do we go first while she follows,

89
00:03:20,197 --> 00:03:22,229
or does she go first
and we wait for five minutes?

90
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,426
Do you think that is feasible?

91
00:03:26,470 --> 00:03:27,360
Chen Youxi,

92
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:28,960
she is a risk.

93
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,190
Why insist on traveling with her?

94
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,870
What kind of risk could she be?

95
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:34,310
She is alone; there are four of us.

96
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:35,403
What's there to worry about?

97
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:38,750
Why insist on going with her?

98
00:03:38,750 --> 00:03:40,520
She has information about the curse.

99
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,120
Fine.

100
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:44,470
Very good.

101
00:03:45,750 --> 00:03:47,470
So, you mean

102
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:48,960
no matter what happens,

103
00:03:49,190 --> 00:03:50,240
you will bring her along?

104
00:03:53,910 --> 00:03:55,120
For now, yes.

105
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,550
Fine.

106
00:03:59,377 --> 00:04:00,457
Then you take her with you.

107
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,640
I will go alone.

108
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:04,550
No.

109
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:17,556
I still have to handle this.

110
00:04:19,830 --> 00:04:20,830
Go after her.

111
00:04:20,830 --> 00:04:21,670
Why?

112
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:24,310
Where did that fighting spirit go?

113
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,760
Wasn't it all because of her?

114
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,160
Now, you just let her go?

115
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,520
Come on.

116
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,190
I give up on you.

117
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:42,190
I can kill a wild wolf
with my bare hands,

118
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:45,270
yet I can't make
the woman I love happy.

119
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:47,560
That is a movie line.

120
00:05:02,583 --> 00:05:04,789
How many times have I said
that woman can't be trusted?

121
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,120
But you insist on believing her.

122
00:05:06,236 --> 00:05:07,369
I've said it countless times.

123
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:08,960
Besides,

124
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,120
this is a team effort.

125
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,270
Not a solo mission.

126
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:14,720
Help.

127
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,920
Help!

128
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:23,870
Help.

129
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,360
Help!

130
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:39,630
Chubby.

131
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:40,590
Chubby!

132
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,920
Chubby, where are you hurt?

133
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:46,790
- Chen.
- Where are you hurt?

134
00:05:49,993 --> 00:05:50,920
Ms. He is not here yet.

135
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,920
Listen to me.

136
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:52,800
Ms. He?

137
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:53,680
What do you mean?

138
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,830
In a moment, follow my lead emotionally.

139
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:57,190
Don't improvise, got it?

140
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,270
Are you crazy?

141
00:05:58,390 --> 00:05:59,323
If you are fine, get up.

142
00:06:00,870 --> 00:06:02,070
About Bai Lingling,

143
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:03,120
what do you plan to do?

144
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:04,870
What about Bai Lingling?

145
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:06,070
What nonsense are you saying?

146
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:08,430
Fool, what is in your head?

147
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:09,920
Don't you know

148
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:10,800
why Ms. He is angry?

149
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,270
Quick.

150
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:18,430
Your hand.

151
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:20,270
Chen,

152
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:24,070
this is as far as I can go with you.

153
00:06:24,870 --> 00:06:26,560
From here on...

154
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,830
What is wrong?

155
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:29,720
Ms. He.

156
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,560
What happened?

157
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:33,560
I picked up a stone.

158
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:36,040
Maybe I was too hungry.

159
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:39,360
I could not resist and licked it.

160
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:43,360
I think I have been poisoned.

161
00:06:44,190 --> 00:06:45,270
Poisoned?

162
00:06:45,950 --> 00:06:48,120
Are you insane?

163
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,950
Why would you lick a stone?

164
00:06:51,310 --> 00:06:53,070
It tastes like chocolate.

165
00:06:53,370 --> 00:06:54,723
If you don't believe me, smell it.

166
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,920
My heart is beating too fast.

167
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:04,560
I can't breathe now.

168
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,750
Chubby, what is wrong?

169
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:10,630
Wrong spot.

170
00:07:11,310 --> 00:07:12,680
Here. The heart.

171
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:13,630
The heart.

172
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,880
- Here?
- The heart.

173
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:17,920
Ms. He,

174
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,160
with my dying breath,

175
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,680
I entrust him to you.

176
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:27,600
I don't ask
that you two grow old together.

177
00:07:27,870 --> 00:07:29,070
I only hope that right now,

178
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:31,190
you can put aside your conflict.

179
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:32,150
Right?

180
00:07:32,270 --> 00:07:35,240
Join hands and have children soon.

181
00:07:36,190 --> 00:07:37,343
That might be a little early.

182
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:41,360
First, get out of this tomb together.

183
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:44,950
Lift the curse on Chen.

184
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:48,040
Then have children.

185
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:51,800
What are you doing?

186
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,120
The Indians have a method.

187
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,870
If someone is poisoned,

188
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:56,680
just let some blood out.

189
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,560
How much?

190
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,920
Not much. Two gallons.

191
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,000
- Two what?
- Come on.

192
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,760
Just half a tank.

193
00:08:04,010 --> 00:08:04,880
No.

194
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,160
Chen has a way to save me.

195
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,000
I believe in TCM.

196
00:08:07,100 --> 00:08:08,000
A way.

197
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,160
A way. TCM.

198
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,920
You...

199
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:16,430
Fool, could you say something?

200
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,870
What a silent fool.

201
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:19,000
What did I just tell you?

202
00:08:19,430 --> 00:08:21,750
Follow my lead emotionally.

203
00:08:21,750 --> 00:08:23,750
And you said nothing.

204
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:25,870
Are you two bored or what?

205
00:08:25,870 --> 00:08:26,830
Three-year-old kids?

206
00:08:29,830 --> 00:08:31,120
Chubby forced me into this.

207
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:32,840
Chen,

208
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,630
that is unfair of you.

209
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,500
You were forced?

210
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:36,550
Then why did I do all this?

211
00:08:36,670 --> 00:08:37,840
Chubby meant well.

212
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,440
Of course.

213
00:08:40,550 --> 00:08:43,200
I even used a stone as an excuse

214
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,750
to put on such a big performance.

215
00:08:44,930 --> 00:08:45,820
Ms. He.

216
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,680
So...

217
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:48,510
Well...

218
00:08:49,030 --> 00:08:50,840
Did you already

219
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,200
figure it out earlier?

220
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:55,600
If you were really about to die,

221
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:57,390
would Chen Youxi still sit there,

222
00:08:57,390 --> 00:08:58,903
listening to such a long final speech?

223
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,030
You are so stupid.

224
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,320
Besides,

225
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,200
do you know what this stone is?

226
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:05,936
Just licking it could poison you?

227
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,600
But this stone is quite magical.

228
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,233
It really smells like chocolate.

229
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:14,150
This should be Wenxiang Jade.

230
00:09:14,313 --> 00:09:15,750
It's said to be an imperial treasure,

231
00:09:15,750 --> 00:09:16,796
also called Jinxiang Jade.

232
00:09:16,816 --> 00:09:18,899
In Prince Gong's Mansion,
there is a treasury vault.

233
00:09:18,910 --> 00:09:19,936
There is one piece inside.

234
00:09:20,319 --> 00:09:22,369
So, this counts as a treasure?

235
00:09:22,380 --> 00:09:24,066
It was discovered
in ancient tombs before.

236
00:09:24,077 --> 00:09:26,139
It first appeared
during the Qin and Han dynasties.

237
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:28,720
I heard it is a kind
of chocolate-scented fossil.

238
00:09:29,059 --> 00:09:31,239
The drier the environment,
the stronger the fragrance.

239
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,720
After friction,
the scent becomes even stronger.

240
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:35,550
You two have said so much.

241
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:36,390
I only want to ask:

242
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:39,600
Is this stone a burial item?

243
00:09:40,790 --> 00:09:42,120
This is just a raw stone.

244
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,600
There are no signs of human carving.

245
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,553
It's not a burial item.

246
00:09:45,030 --> 00:09:46,790
Then why would it appear here?

247
00:09:47,510 --> 00:09:48,350
Look.

248
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:50,120
I walked all the way here

249
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,360
and did not take

250
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,270
or touch anything.

251
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:54,240
This stone

252
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,000
is not a burial item anyway.

253
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:58,670
I want to keep it as a souvenir.

254
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,390
It is also for the two of you.

255
00:10:00,790 --> 00:10:02,960
If you argue again in the future,

256
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,086
I will put this between you
and let you smell it.

257
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,240
Once you smell...

258
00:10:06,330 --> 00:10:07,200
Well.

259
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,790
I will keep it for now.

260
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:10,320
Come to me if you need it.

261
00:10:10,630 --> 00:10:11,470
Chen.

262
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,720
There are so many mechanisms here.

263
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,750
You can't act alone anymore.

264
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,080
I don't want to walk with you.

265
00:10:24,270 --> 00:10:25,670
I think acting alone is great.

266
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,040
Why?

267
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,390
Because of Bai Lingling?

268
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,080
Yes.

269
00:10:31,630 --> 00:10:33,240
I just feel she has another agenda.

270
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,486
Even if she does,

271
00:10:34,497 --> 00:10:35,910
she doesn't even have a helper now.

272
00:10:35,910 --> 00:10:36,750
What could she do?

273
00:10:37,030 --> 00:10:38,510
Then why keep a ticking time bomb

274
00:10:38,510 --> 00:10:39,480
by your side?

275
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:41,000
We can't just let her die.

276
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,566
What does her death have to do with you?

277
00:10:43,050 --> 00:10:43,910
You two,

278
00:10:44,030 --> 00:10:45,200
stop arguing, alright?

279
00:10:45,550 --> 00:10:46,390
Ms. He,

280
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,390
if you really don't trust Bai Lingling,

281
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,440
why don't we

282
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,790
just ask her directly?

283
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,960
Do you think she'd tell the truth?

284
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,200
Who am I?

285
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:58,510
Just leave it to me.

286
00:10:58,870 --> 00:10:59,710
Let's go.

287
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:15,960
What was that sound?

288
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:38,120
We took you in

289
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,200
out of kindness, you know.

290
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,750
Just follow us honestly.

291
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:42,790
Why do you keep annoying Ms. He?

292
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,510
She is the one who is jealous.

293
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:45,750
Not my business.

294
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:47,080
Not your business?

295
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:47,920
A few words from you

296
00:11:47,940 --> 00:11:49,600
caused their fight.

297
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,320
One bad ladle ruins
the whole pot of soup.

298
00:11:52,790 --> 00:11:53,630
Don't move.

299
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:54,480
Let go of me.

300
00:11:54,520 --> 00:11:55,370
What are you doing?

301
00:11:55,390 --> 00:11:56,600
I am doing this for your good.

302
00:12:02,150 --> 00:12:03,030
Listen.

303
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:04,630
Answer

304
00:12:04,750 --> 00:12:05,600
all my questions.

305
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:07,030
If you refuse to tell the truth,

306
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,200
I will tie you up right here

307
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,670
and let you fend for yourself.

308
00:12:11,270 --> 00:12:12,150
Chen Youxi,

309
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:13,960
is this how you treat a friend?

310
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,270
We are not friends.

311
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:22,720
Earlier, you told Huang Long
that anyone could die

312
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:24,960
except Chen Youxi and Ms. He.

313
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:25,920
What did you mean?

314
00:12:27,270 --> 00:12:28,480
If Chen Youxi died,

315
00:12:28,510 --> 00:12:29,510
how could I move forward?

316
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:31,800
What about Ms. He?

317
00:12:31,810 --> 00:12:32,650
If she died,

318
00:12:32,660 --> 00:12:33,916
would Chen Youxi still help me?

319
00:12:35,270 --> 00:12:36,790
That still doesn't make sense.

320
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:38,600
If Chubby and I died,

321
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:40,120
he'd also fight you to the death.

322
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,040
Are you sure?

323
00:12:44,870 --> 00:12:46,720
She is really infuriating.

324
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,630
Sowing discord.

325
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:49,480
You are still arrogant
even while tied up.

326
00:12:49,510 --> 00:12:51,120
Enough, Bai Lingling.

327
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,360
Stop being vague.

328
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,550
Just tell us directly

329
00:12:53,630 --> 00:12:55,360
what you need Chen Youxi and me

330
00:12:55,630 --> 00:12:56,480
to help you with.

331
00:12:56,630 --> 00:12:58,270
You already know

332
00:12:58,550 --> 00:12:59,550
why I need Chen Youxi.

333
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:01,600
As for you,

334
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,480
you are knowledgeable

335
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,440
and highly accomplished in semiotics.

336
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,150
According to my research,

337
00:13:07,510 --> 00:13:08,720
that eyeball symbol

338
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:10,550
has some connection with semiotics.

339
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,550
Once we find the real main hall,

340
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:13,470
bringing you along

341
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:15,550
might help us solve

342
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:17,150
the mystery of the curse.

343
00:13:21,550 --> 00:13:23,240
I think that long speech just now

344
00:13:23,510 --> 00:13:24,750
made a lot of sense.

345
00:13:25,150 --> 00:13:26,196
Do you even have a stance?

346
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,440
Well.

347
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:29,240
If you are still not reassured,

348
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:30,750
you can keep me tied up.

349
00:13:30,870 --> 00:13:32,320
If you still want to break the curse

350
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,553
and continue moving forward,

351
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:35,153
there will be a time when you need me.

352
00:13:39,630 --> 00:13:40,470
How about this?

353
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:41,910
I will keep an eye on her.

354
00:13:44,870 --> 00:13:45,720
Alright then.

355
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:49,000
Sorry about this, Miss Bai.

356
00:13:49,270 --> 00:13:50,110
Move.

357
00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:55,510
Chen,

358
00:13:55,610 --> 00:13:56,490
I really want to know

359
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:58,360
how the two of you got up here.

360
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,910
We fell into the Bagua chamber

361
00:14:02,390 --> 00:14:04,240
and got trapped in the Qian chamber.

362
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:55,720
How did you manage it?

363
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:59,150
Power and wealth fade away

364
00:14:59,150 --> 00:15:00,360
with time.

365
00:15:05,630 --> 00:15:07,200
Only wisdom and knowledge

366
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,720
can endure forever.

367
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:13,840
These tomb builders, back then,

368
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:16,240
were seen as craftsmen,

369
00:15:16,390 --> 00:15:17,270
laborers,

370
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:18,150
the lowest class,

371
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:19,840
unworthy of high society.

372
00:15:20,550 --> 00:15:22,840
Yet every mechanism I encountered

373
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:25,390
in this tomb shows their mastery

374
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:26,480
of astronomy,

375
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:27,630
Feng Shui,

376
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:28,480
numerology,

377
00:15:28,490 --> 00:15:29,390
physics,

378
00:15:29,550 --> 00:15:30,840
mechanics, and more.

379
00:15:31,550 --> 00:15:32,790
If they lived today,

380
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,000
they would be scientists,

381
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:36,790
architects,

382
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:38,080
and astronomers.

383
00:15:39,670 --> 00:15:42,120
Their value far exceeds

384
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:44,240
that of the imperial nobles
who enslaved them.

385
00:15:44,550 --> 00:15:45,390
They are the ones

386
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:49,390
who truly deserve
to be remembered in history.

387
00:16:01,270 --> 00:16:02,600
If what you say is true,

388
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:03,790
then this tomb

389
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:05,790
has several floors.

390
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:09,320
With all the slopes and stairs,

391
00:16:09,630 --> 00:16:11,480
it's hard to say
what the exact structure is.

392
00:16:12,510 --> 00:16:15,080
But that last mechanism was interesting.

393
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:16,390
Most mechanisms

394
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:17,870
are built to stop tomb raiders.

395
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:20,630
Yet the last one
not only had a solution,

396
00:16:21,030 --> 00:16:23,000
but it felt like it was communicating
with Chen.

397
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:26,000
An emotional resonance is
just my personal feeling.

398
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,550
But for the tomb builder

399
00:16:27,561 --> 00:16:29,310
to express himself
through mechanism design

400
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:31,440
in such a grand tomb

401
00:16:32,030 --> 00:16:33,870
is truly unheard of.

402
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,630
What are you doing? Do you want to die?

403
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:42,440
Help.

404
00:16:42,790 --> 00:16:44,720
Police station. Call the police.

405
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:45,560
What?

406
00:16:45,870 --> 00:16:46,710
Call the police.

407
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:05,020
♪A tiny ark sails;
the sky opens its eyes♪

408
00:17:06,700 --> 00:17:10,380
♪Stillness in motion,
the earth plays its chord♪

409
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:16,020
♪A leaf falls;
we cross through time and space♪

410
00:17:16,170 --> 00:17:23,170
♪In a blink, all things rest
upon our hands♪

411
00:17:23,730 --> 00:17:34,750
♪La la♪

412
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:43,490
♪No line divides the border♪

413
00:17:43,930 --> 00:17:46,270
♪Nothing limits your performance♪

414
00:17:46,270 --> 00:17:48,640
♪Everything shows perfect harmony♪

415
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:51,330
♪Love circles the sky,
the earth, and our faith♪

416
00:17:52,830 --> 00:17:54,540
♪Hey hey hey♪

417
00:17:55,870 --> 00:17:57,690
♪Hey hey hey♪

418
00:18:00,340 --> 00:18:01,340
♪Hey hey♪

419
00:18:01,490 --> 00:18:02,490
♪Hey hey♪

420
00:18:03,950 --> 00:18:05,030
♪Hey hey♪

421
00:18:06,660 --> 00:18:10,860
♪Step into the galaxy of colors♪

422
00:18:11,450 --> 00:18:15,160
♪Stars connect our hearts as one♪

423
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,660
♪No difference between you and me♪

424
00:18:19,940 --> 00:18:22,270
♪No lead or side role on this stage♪

425
00:18:22,270 --> 00:18:24,480
♪A perfect life is something we share♪

426
00:18:24,700 --> 00:18:26,980
♪Love declares across the sky and earth♪

427
00:18:27,910 --> 00:18:32,700
♪Huo la yi ya, huo la yi ya♪

428
00:18:32,700 --> 00:18:37,550
♪Time and space go beyond all bounds♪

429
00:18:37,550 --> 00:18:42,400
♪Huo la yi ya, huo la yi ya♪

430
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:44,490
♪This is our world♪

431
00:18:44,490 --> 00:18:49,520
♪Shining lives bring the change♪

432
00:18:54,050 --> 00:18:56,610
♪In a blink, to forever♪
